{
  "fadeOut": 1.5,
  "fadein": 1.5,
  "scripts": [
    {
      "dir": 1,
      "actor": 307060,
      "side": 2,
      "bgm": "nagato-boss",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Okay, I'm really, really sorry for trying to rouse you from your slumber...!",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "stopbgm": true
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Sensing a fiery fury within the eyes of the girl, Zuikaku panicked and began pleading for forgiveness.",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "You must be Zuikaku of the 5th Carrier Division. What business have you with me?"
    },
    {
      "actor": 307060,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "... Head on the nail! You see, we need you on our side!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I refuse!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 307060,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Could you at least try it before you say no?!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I was tasked with ensuring the Sacred Sakura's safety. I shall remain here till my body turns to dust."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305060,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Nagato, you..."
    },
    {
      "actor": 307060,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Did you make that decision of your own accord? Or was it forced on you?"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I... It is for the sake of the Sakura Empire and her people, and to atone for my sins. My say is irrelevant."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "You fool!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 30,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.1,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "W-what?!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Do you not see how frivolous it is to sit here and rot away when a battleship of your caliber is more desirable than ever in these changing times?!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 15,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.1,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I-is that..."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 15,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.1,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Is that you, Mikasa?!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Your 41 centimeter cannons make whole nations quiver, your bridge towers to the heavens, your armor deflects shells like they were stones..."
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Trying to hide her envy, Mikasa whispered: \"... My envy of you cannot be adequately expressed! You are the finest example of a battleship!\"",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Nagato was trying to maintain her dignified appearance, but humbled by Mikasa's words, she loosened up.",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I-it's not as great as you think... But why are you here, Mikasa?"
    },
    {
      "actor": 307060,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Uh, it's a long story, so why don't you come with us and we'll explain it on the way..."
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "However, Nagato ignored what Zuikaku was saying.",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "M-Mikasa, ever since I became the Combined Fleet's flagship, I've been trying to be like you..."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I tried to be a magnificent flagship... And yet..."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Say no more. Have a battle with me."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 30,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.1,
          "number": 1,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Huh...?"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "I needed only one look at your cannons to know it with certainty: you haven't fired them as much as once since your birth."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Ah...!?"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Mikasa's remark caused a single tear to form in the corner of one of Nagato's eyes.",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Battleships should know dearly the smell of the sea and gunpowder, not of trees and their own rusting hulls. I can't stand to see my successor stuck in a place like this."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Sometimes, a battle can offer more insight into a person's character than a thousand of their words."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305110,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "You there, you must be her little sister. Why not join us for a bout?"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305060,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "Sure! Hehehe~ I've been waiting so long for this day!"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "say": "......"
    },
    {
      "stopbgm": true,
      "sequence": [
        [
          "Thou shalt not touch a human, for they would tarnish thy divinity.",
          0
        ],
        [
          "Thou shalt not smile, for thou must maintain thy dignity.",
          3
        ],
        [
          "Thou shalt not forget: the Creator is your only God.",
          6
        ]
      ],
      "mode": 1
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "blackBg": true,
      "say": "Because I was made by humans, I desire bonds just like them.\t"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "blackBg": true,
      "say": "Dignity alone won't make my people admire me. At times, I must smile, too."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "blackBg": true,
      "say": "O, Creator, I beg of you: grant me new life as someone whom my people can believe in with all their heart."
    },
    {
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "bgm": "nagato-boss",
      "flashout": {
        "alpha": [
          0,
          1
        ],
        "black": true,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "dir": 1,
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "Very well! Lacking in experience as I may be, I shall hold nothing back!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "withoutPainting": true,
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nagato4"
    },
    {
      "dir": 1,
      "actor": 305050,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "I am Nagato, Big Seven of the Sakura Empire! Prepare yourself!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "withoutPainting": true,
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_nagato4"
    }
  ],
